IndicatorDesc: Proportion of population using safely managed sanitation services, including a hand-washing facility with soap and water
SeriesDesc: Proportion of population using safely managed sanitation services, by urban/rural (%)
Source: WHO/UNICEF Joint Monitoring Programme for Water Supply, Sanitation and Hygiene (2017)
